text: James Varni Panetta ( ; born October 1, 1969) is an American lawyer, politician, and former Navy intelligence officer from the state of California. A member of the Democratic Party, he is the U.S. representative for California's 19th congressional district. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from California Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
